(7, 'Davidmed', 'no.reply.UweVincent@gmail.com', '81968946132', 'Do you desire to entice more customers for your business?', 'Good morning! sastrabhinnekakarya.co.id, \r\nI came across sastrabhinnekakarya.co.id while browsing websites. \r\nOur system allows sending outreach messages through website contact forms. \r\nCompanies often use contact pages to present their offers. \r\n  \r\n  \r\nFeel free to reach out if you would like details. \r\n \r\nThanks and have a great day. \r\nContact us. \r\nTelegram - https://t.me/FeedbackFormEU \r\nWhatsApp - +375259112693 \r\nWhatsApp  https://wa.me/+375259112693', 'new', NULL, '2026-05-27 12:36:50', '2026-05-27 12:36:50'),
